data.name: grdOUT1001.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT DECODE(NVL(A.RESER_YN, 'N'), 'Y', 'N', 'Y') JUBSU, NVL(A.RESER_YN, 'N') RESER_YN, A.JUBSU_TIME JINRYO_TIME, FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.GWA, A.NAEWON_DATE) GWA_NAME, FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.DOCTOR, A.NAEWON_DATE) DOCTOR_NAME, FN_BAS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('NAEWON_YN', A.NAEWON_YN) NAEWON_YN_NAME, A.BUNHO BUNHO, A.NAEWON_DATE NAEWON_DATE, A.GWA GWA, A.DOCTOR DOCTOR, A.NAEWON_TYPE NAEWON_TYPE, A.JUBSU_NO JUBSU_NO, A.PKOUT1001 PK_NAEWON, A.NAEWON_YN ORDER_END_YN FROM OUT0101 B, OUT1001 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.NAEWON_DATE = :f_naewon_date AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND ( A.GWA <> :f_gwa OR A.DOCTOR <> :f_doctor ) AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.BUNHO = A.BUNHO AND ( ( :f_naewon_yn = '%' ) OR ( :f_naewon_yn = 'Y' AND A.NAEWON_YN = 'E' ) OR ( :f_naewon_yn = 'N' AND A.NAEWON_YN != 'E' ) ) ORDER BY 3

data.name: grdOCS1001.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.JU_SANG_YN , A.SANG_CODE , A.SER , A.PRE_MODIFIER_NAME||A.SANG_NAME||A.POST_MODIFIER_NAME DIS_SANG_NAME, A.SANG_START_DATE , A.SANG_END_DATE , A.SANG_END_SAYU , A.BUNHO , A.NAEWON_DATE , A.GWA , A.DOCTOR , A.NAEWON_TYPE , A.JUBSU_NO , A.BUNHO||TO_CHAR(A.NAEWON_DATE,'YYYYMMDD')||A.GWA||A.DOCTOR||A.NAEWON_TYPE||LTRIM(TO_CHAR(A.JUBSU_NO)) PK_ORDER, A.SANG_NAME , A.PRE_MODIFIER1 , A.PRE_MODIFIER2 , A.PRE_MODIFIER3 , A.PRE_MODIFIER4 , A.PRE_MODIFIER5 , A.PRE_MODIFIER6 , A.PRE_MODIFIER7 , A.PRE_MODIFIER8 , A.PRE_MODIFIER9 , A.PRE_MODIFIER10 , A.PRE_MODIFIER_NAME , A.POST_MODIFIER1 , A.POST_MODIFIER2 , A.POST_MODIFIER3 , A.POST_MODIFIER4 , A.POST_MODIFIER5 , A.POST_MODIFIER6 , A.POST_MODIFIER7 , A.POST_MODIFIER8 , A.POST_MODIFIER9 , A.POST_MODIFIER10 , A.POST_MODIFIER_NAME, DECODE(A.SANG_END_DATE, NULL, 'N', 'Y') END_YN FROM OUTSANG A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.GWA = :f_gwa AND :f_naewon_date BETWEEN A.SANG_START_DATE AND NVL(A.SANG_END_DATE, TO_DATE('99981231', 'YYYYMMDD')) ORDER BY A.SANG_START_DATE, A.SER
